# --- Secrets / credentials: never commit ---
**/connection.RData
**/connection_old.RData
.Renviron
**/.Renviron
*.pem
*.ppk

# --- R session / IDE state ---
.Rhistory
**/.Rhistory
.Rproj.user/
**/.Rproj.user/
.RData

# --- renv vendored package library (regenerate with renv::restore()) ---
**/renv/library/
**/renv/staging/
**/renv/sandbox/
**/renv/python/

# --- rsconnect deployment metadata (account/app IDs, not app code) ---
**/rsconnect/

# --- Dropbox sync internals ---
**/.dropbox.cache/

# --- OS cruft ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Data caches, reports, and office docs: not source, kept locally only ---
*.rds
*.RData
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.docx
*.pptm
*.html
